import { Form, FormControl, Button, Modal, Row, Col } from 'react-bootstrap';
import React,{ useContext } from 'react';
import { ModeContext } from './ModeContext';
function Mode(props) {
  const [show, setShow] = useContext(ModeContext);
  return (
     <Modal show={show} onHide={() => setShow(false)} style={{position:'fixed', zIndex:'999999999999'}}>
        <Modal.Header closeButton>
          <Modal.Title>Ruqun Aljazeera Services Provider</Modal.Title>
        </Modal.Header>
        <Modal.Body>
          <Row>
            <Col xs={12} md={12}>
        <Form className="ContactForm" >
                <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="exampleForm.ControlInput1">
                  <Form.Control type="email" placeholder="name@example.com" />
                </Form.Group>
                <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="exampleForm.ControlInput1">
                  <Form.Control type="tel" placeholder="tel: +971501234567" />
                </Form.Group>
                <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="exampleForm.ControlInput1">
                  <Form.Control type="text" placeholder="Your full name" />
                </Form.Group>
                <Form.Group className="mb-3" controlId="exampleForm.ControlTextarea1">
                  <Form.Control as="textarea" rows={3} />
                </Form.Group>
                <Button>Submit</Button>
              </Form>
              </Col>
          </Row>
        </Modal.Body>
      </Modal>
    

  );
}

export default Mode;
